  schema:name "Stories in the Spotlight - Show/Spectacle";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Performance-Only ticket</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This $100 ticket is your opportunity to experience the performance portion of the annual Centaur Gala. Join Terry DiMonte, Ranee Lee and her band, Joey Elias, artists from Centaur’s upcoming season, and fellow theatre lovers for a joyful celebration of live performance. <span class=\"BoldText\">This ticket does not come with a tax-receipt</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>To attend the cocktail dînatoire as well as the show, buy your tickets <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.centaurtheatre.com/EventAvailability?EventId=18601\">here</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Billet pour le spectacle seulement</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ce billet de 100 $ vous donne l'occasion d'assister au spectacle lors du gala annuel du Centaur. Joignez-vous à Terry DiMonte, Ranee Lee et son groupe, Joey Elias, aux artistes de la prochaine saison du Centaur et à d'autres passionnés de théâtre pour une célébration joyeuse du spectacle vivant. <span class=\"BoldText\">Ce billet n'est pas accompagné d'un reçu fiscal.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Pour assister au cocktail dînatoire et au spectacle, achetez vos billets<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.centaurtheatre.com/EventAvailability?EventId=18601\"> ici</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
